
Section 8 - read_verb_file

#include <verb.h>

read_verb_file(filename)

string filename;

This removes all the verbs from the calling object, and then adds new verbs
as defined in the verb file specified by filename.

The format of this file is:

verb VerbName,FunctionName
xverb XVerbName,FunctionName

The 'verb' command will add a regular verb; the 'xverb' command adds an
xverb. Blank lines and lines beginning with '#' are ignored.

See Also: add_verb(7), add_xverb(7)

